### Transpiration
- Water is absorbed by plants and lost through pores of leaves
	- Transpirational loss
	- Contributes significant amount of water vapor to the atmosphere, and causes more rain

	- HOWEVER, transpiration increases the rate of water absorption in the roots

### Evaporation
- The evaporation of water from the soil around plants
